\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs20 New hidden sub control: \b StswSubError \b0 (used in box controls to show validation errors).\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New base class: \b StswBoxBase \b0 (for box controls).\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New converter: \b StswRadioConverter \b0 (for RadioBox based controls).\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New extension: \b RemoveBy \b0 (to remove multiple items from IList).\par

