\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b\fs20 IStswBoxControl \b0 interface has been extended. All box controls have 2 new properties: "Errors", "HasError", and 1 less property: "IsErrorVisible".\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs24 Bugfixes:\par

\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b\fs20 StswBindingList \b0 can be sorted now (for example in \b StswDataGrid \b0 when clicked on column).\f1\lang21\par

