\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs20 There is new category for Stsw controls named "File" that includes 1 new control: \b StswFilePicker \b0 used to select either file or directory path.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New controls: \b StswHyperlinkButton\b0 , \b StswShiftButton\b0 , \b StswTimedSwitch\b0 , \b StswDataPager\b0 , \b StswTimePicker\b0 , \b StswFilePicker\b0 , \b StswMediaPlayer\b0 , \b StswMenuItem\b0 , \b StswInfoBadge\b0 , \b StswInfoBar\b0 , \b StswWindowBar\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New control style: \b StswContextMenu\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New interface: \b IStswBoxControl\b0 . \b IStswComponentControl \b0 renamed into \b IStswSubControl\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New converter: \b StswListFromRangeConverter\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New extensions: \b ToImageSource\b0 , \b GetNextValue \b0 (instead of \b GetNextEnumValue \b0 function).\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New functions: \b SplitStringByLines\b0 , \b RemoveFromParent\b0 .\par

