\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs20 External library called "NewtonsoftJson" is no longer used.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b StswNavigation \b0 and \b StswNavigationElement \b0 have been reworked.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b StswSidePanel \b0 can be set to be always visible.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}"Components" controls category renamed into "Subs" controls. All component controls changed prefix to "Sub". All properties for components renamed into "SubControls".\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b StswShifter \b0 renamed into \b StswDirectionViewer\b0 . \b StswLogPanel \b0 renamed into \b StswInfoPanel\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b StswHeader \b0 and all sub controls now has property "IsContentVisible" instead of "ContentVisibility".\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Part of \b StswWindow\b0 's functionality moved to new control \b StswWindowBar\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}A few changes in Stsw enums.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}A few changes in theme brush key names.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b StswMailboxModel \b0 implements INotifyPropertyChanged now.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs24 Bugfixes:\par

\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs20 Bugfix translation for \b StswColorBox\b0 's tab headers.\f1\lang21\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\f0\lang1045 Going into fullscreen mode should properly activate and focus window.\f1\lang21\par

