\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b\fs20 StswCalendar \b0 no longer allows to select date that is not between minimum and maximum range. "Today" button becomes disabled when current date is not in minimum and maximum range.\par

