\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b\fs20 StswFilterBox \b0 have "FilterMenuMode" property for filter mode button. \b StswFilterMode \b0 enum no longer have "None" value.\par

