\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b\fs20 StswCalendar \b0 had mini-rework that should simplify its code with template and overall make it works better. \b StswCalendar \b0 also has new button to select today's date.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b StswDropButton\b0 , \b StswSplitButton\b0 , \b StswComboBox\b0 , \b StswSelectionBox\b0  and all component buttons\b  \b0 have simplified template. \b StswDataGrid \b0 is finally using its own template. \b StswDropButton \b0 and \b StswSplitButton \b0 are derived from ItemsControl class.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}"IsTabStop" property is set to false in propably all places in Stsw controls where it is needed.\par
