{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b StswComponentRebutton \b0 has been renamed into \b StswComponentRepeater\b0 . \b IStswSelectionItem \b0 has been renamed to \b IStswSelection\b0 . \b IStswCollectionItem \b0 has property renamed from "ErrorMessage" to "ItemMessage". "PopupBorderThickness" property has been renamed to "PopupThickness" in all Stsw controls that use it.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}"MaxDropDownHeight" property's default value increased from 120 to 140 in all Stsw controls that use it.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Debug messages (\b StswMessageDialog\b0 , \b StswLogPanel\b0 ) has different icon with original one removed completely. \b StswDataGrid\b0 's items with filled "ItemMessage" property will show information icon in its special column.\par
