\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs20 .NET version increased from 5 to 6.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}All controls and helping classes in library has been renamed and use "Stsw" prefix. Some of them have also completely changed names like \b ExtDatePicker \b0 -> \b StswCalendarPicker\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Many controls have been completely reworked, those with most changes are: \b StswColumnFilter\b0  (original name: ColumnFilter), \b StswHeader\b0  (original name: Header), \b LoadingCircle\b0 , \b StswProgressBar\b0  (original name: ExtProgressBar), \b StswWindow\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Completely new controls: \b ClippingBorder \b0 (to properly render content when CornerRadius is used), \b StswNavigation\b0 , \b StswNavigationButton\b0 , \b StswPasswordBox\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New extension methods: \b AsBytes\b0 , \b ToNullable\b0 , \b ToStswDictionary\b0 , \b TrimEnd\b0  (with string as parameter), \b TrimStart\b0  (with string as parameter), \b TryMultipleTimes\b0  (that tries to execute an action or function multiple times with a specified interval between each try until it succeeds or reaches a maximum number of tries).\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New classes: \b StswCollection \b0 (extended version of ObservableCollection - it notifies even if single item's property has changed and can contain info about states of items), \b StswDictionary\b0  (have INotifyProperty implemented and can be binded in a way that creates new key if it did not existed yet), \b StswExport\b0  (for exporting data to Excel file using "ClosedXML" library),\b  StswMC \b0 (meant to store mail configurations and sending mails), \b StswRelayCommand\b0  (have ICommand implemented and is meant to be binded to control command properties), \b StswSimpleModel \b0 (meant to be model for item sources in combo boxes).\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New converters: \b conv_Add \b0 (that adds number from parameter to target number), \b conv_Calculate \b0 (that uses DataTable's compute method), \b conv_ColorBrightness\b0 , \b conv_IfElse\b0  (that displays one of two texts based on bool result of comparing), \b conv_NullToUnset\b0 , \b conv_Sum \b0 (that allows to sum field in list of class elements).\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Collection (7000+) of vector icons in new \b StswIcons \b0 static class.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b StswDataGrid \b0 has new special column for showing and clearing filters and showing row details.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b StswWindow \b0 has now fullscreen mode.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}TextBox based controls have placeholder functionality.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New \b AppStart \b0 method meant to be put on application startup. This method sets all starting configuration needed for application to work properly if it is using Stsw controls and some of helpers.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}New project for library testing called \b TestApp\b0 . This version of test app has 3 simple modules: Database, Contractors, LibraryTests.\par

