\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs20 Themes are now based on external library called "DynamicAero2". There are two themes: \b Light \b0 and \b Dark\b0 , with possibility to auto select one of them based on system theme.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Many controls and functions have been adjusted to use them comfortably in MVVM.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Controls are now built on templates in styles in resource dictionaries.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Most of controls have "CornerRadius" property now.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}\b VM \b0 renamed into \b StswObservableObject\b0 . \b StswObservableObject \b0 have method called "SetProperty" that can be used in simple way in property setters.\par
