{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Controls like \b DataGridImage\b0 , \b ExtMenuItem\b0  and \b IconButton \b0 have been removed. Methods like \b AddCharBeforeUpperLetters\b0  have been removed.\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Converter \b conv_Size\b0  has been renamed to \b conv_Multiply\b0 . Extension method named \b ToList \b0 has been renamed to \b AsList\b0 . Method extension \b GetVisualChild \b0 renamed to \b FindVisualChild\b0 .\par
{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}Method \b ConvertTo \b0 made into extension method. Method \b LoadImage \b0 made into extension method named \b AsImage\b0 .\par
